Name: Description
Obs-class: An operating model component that controls the observation model

Name: Function call
Obs-class: Objects can be created by calls of the form new('Obs')

Name: Name
Obs-class: The name of the observation model object

Name: Cobs
Obs-class: Log-normal catch observation error expressed as a coefficient of variation (uniform distribution)

Name: Cbiascv
Obs-class: A coefficient of variation controlling the sampling of bias in catch observations for each simulation (uniform distribution)

Name: CAA_nsamp
Obs-class: Number of catch-at-age observation per time step (uniform distribution)

Name: CAA_ESS
Obs-class: Effective sample size (independent age draws) of the multinomial catch-at-age observation error model (uniform distribution)

Name: CAL_nsamp
Obs-class: Number of catch-at-length observation per time step (uniform distribution)

Name: CAL_ESS
Obs-class: Effective sample size (independent length draws) of the multinomial catch-at-length observation error model (uniform distribution)

Name: CALcv
Obs-class: Lognormal, variability in the length at age (uniform distribution)

Name: Iobs
Obs-class: Observation error in the relative abundance indices expressed as a coefficient of variation (uniform distribution)

Name: Mcv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of natural mortality rate sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (Mcv)(uniform distribution)

Name: Kcv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of growth parameter k sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (Kcv)(uniform distribution)

Name: t0cv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of t0 sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (t0cv)(uniform distribution)

Name: Linfcv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of maximum length sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (Linfcv)(uniform distribution)

Name: LFCcv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of lenght at first capture sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (LFCcv)(uniform distribution)

Name: LFScv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of length-at-fully selection sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (LFScv)(uniform distribution)

Name: B0cv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of maximum lengthunfished biomass sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (B0cv)(uniform distribution)

Name: FMSYcv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of FMSY sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (FMSYcv)(uniform distribution)

Name: FMSY_Mcv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of FMSY/M sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (FMSY_cv)(uniform distribution)

Name: BMSY_B0cv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of BMsY relative to unfished sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (BMSY_B0cv)(uniform distribution)

Name: rcv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of intrinsic rate of increase sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (rcv)(uniform distribution)

Name: LenMcv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of length at 50 percent maturity sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (A50cv)(uniform distribution)

Name: Dbiascv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of stock depletion sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (Linfcv)(uniform distribution)

Name: Dcv
Obs-class: Imprecision in the prescription of stock depletion among years, expressed as a coefficient of variation (uniform distribution)

Name: Btbias
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of current stock biomass sampled from a uniform-log distribution with range (Btbias)(uniform distribution)

Name: Btcv
Obs-class: Imprecision in the prescription of current stock biomass among years expressed as a coefficient of variation (uniform distribution)

Name: Fcurbiascv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in the prescription of current fishing mortality rate sampled from a log-normal distribution with coefficient of variation (Fcurcv)(uniform distribution)

Name: Fcurcv
Obs-class: Imprecision in the prescription of current fishing mortality rate among years expressed as a coefficient of variation (uniform distribution)

Name: hcv
Obs-class: Persistent bias in steepness (uniform distribution)

Name: Icv
Obs-class: Observation error in realtive abundance index expressed as a coefficient of variation (uniform distirbution)

Name: maxagecv
Obs-class: Bias in the prescription of maximum age (uniform distribution)

Name: beta
Obs-class: A parameter controlling hyperstability/hyperdepletion. I^beta therefore values below 1 lead to hyperstability (an index that decreases slower than true abundance) and values above 1 lead to hyperdepletion (an index that decreases more rapidly than true abundance)(uniform distribution)

Name: Reccv
Obs-class: Bias in the knowledge of recent recruitment strength (uniform distribution)

Name: Irefcv
Obs-class: Bias in the knowledge of the relative abundance index at BMSY (uniform distribution)

Name: Brefcv
Obs-class: Bias in the knowledge of BMSY (uniform distribution)

Name: Crefcv
Obs-class: Bias in the knowledge of MSY(uniform distribution)
